caption: Went to the Sunny Isles location for lunch and was seated by whom we believe was a manager-Rene.  After being seated and reviewing menu, we noticed that we were given the dinner menu.  We arrived at 1:40 and completed reviewing the dinner menu at 1:45.  Asked if there was a lunch menu due to the fact our party did not want large portions.  Lunch menu is served 12 to 2 PM, I know this after going to the South Miami restaurant many times.  Rene appeared to be agitated, after he realized he should have given us the lunch menu and provides us the dinner menu which would have resulted in much higher costs for our party.  Ordered drinks and service was non existent from Rene and he hurried us along when we ordered drinks of which my wife could not even indicate she wanted wine.  We called another waitress who had served my wife and a large group of friends on previous visits to this location.  Never saw Rene again for service.
